                            <comment id="13905874" author="tilman" created="Wed, 19 Feb 2014 18:59:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the idea to try older versions, I tested with several recent revisions and found that 1561111 is ok but 1561191 is not ok.&lt;br/&gt;
